   <section id="calculate-your-environmental-impact" class="why_matter content-paragraph grid_wrapper paragraph-container">
    <div class="species_image ">
        <picture >
                <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/content_slide_image/public/2023-07/calculate%20impact_black.png?h=a955cd85&amp;itok=KjVClxmS" width="1000" height="600" alt="My Footprint App - Calculate Impact" class="image-style-content-slide-image" />




        </picture>

                <div class="copyright--image">© WWF-UK</div>
            </div>
    <div class="content content--padded species_image_contain">
            <h3>

<div class="field field--display_title">
  <h2>Calculate your environmental impact</h2>
</div>
</h3>
            <div class="rich-text-wrapper">
          <p>Extreme weather, forest fires and the global pandemic have made us all stop and consider - what we can start to do to help our planet.</p><p>We’ve seen the devastating impact that human activity can have on the natural world, but it doesn’t have to be this way. We can build a better world by all making small changes in our everyday lives.&nbsp;</p><p>Start by calculating your footprint to really understand your personal impact.&nbsp;</p>

      </div>
              

          <div class="btn-wrap">
                          
                   

     <div class="btn-wrap--item">
     <a href="#my-footprint-logo"  class="btn anchor_link  btn--white" ga-on="click" ga-event-category="CTAButton" ga-event-action="click - #my-footprint-logo" ga-event-label=" Calculate your environmental impact  Download the app">
         Download the app
     </a>
     </div>

     
     
      
     </div>
          </div>
</section>
