   <section id="understand-your-impact" class="why_matter content-paragraph grid_wrapper paragraph-container">
    <div class="species_image species_image_reverse">
        <picture >
                <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/content_slide_image/public/2023-07/footprint-black_0.png?h=a955cd85&amp;itok=vgXVU7PI" width="1000" height="600" alt="My Footprint App - Footprint" class="image-style-content-slide-image" />




        </picture>

                <div class="copyright--image">© WWF-UK</div>
            </div>
    <div class="content content--padded content_reverse">
            <h3>

<div class="field field--display_title">
  <h2>Understand your impact</h2>
</div>
</h3>
            <div class="rich-text-wrapper">
          <p>WWF-UK’s <strong>My Footprint app</strong> is your hub for positive change. Using this app is a step in the right direction to help our planet and keep you motivated to make sustainable choices.&nbsp;</p><p>Once you calculate your impact, you'll be able to see how you compare to the world and UK average, as well as understand which parts of your lifestyle contribute the most to your score.&nbsp;</p>

      </div>
              

          <div class="btn-wrap">
                          
                   

